title: Finding Success In The Beauty Industry
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew interview Jess Hallock who is a successful stylist and salon owner in Arizona. She has taken her name and grown it into a full fledged brand so she gives us tips on how she started out and also tells some funny stories that have happened along the way.
